{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tooluse_Q2m3gtW8tieMYHuzut0vos","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t---\n2\tid: task_15_volume_price_contraction_breakout\n3\tname: 缩量整理后放量突破形态识别\n4\tcategory: complex_volume_price_pattern\n5\tgrading_type: hybrid\n6\ttimeout_seconds: 480\n7\tgrading_weights:\n8\t  automated: 0.4\n9\t  llm_judge: 0.6\n10\tworkspace_files: []\n11\t---\n12\t\n13\t## Prompt\n14\t\n15\t在创业板中找出以 2024-07-15 为截止交易日的前60个交易日内出现\"缩量整理后放量突破\"形态的股票，条件：\n16\t\n17\t1. **缩量期**：存在连续至少8天的缩量期，每天成交量均低于60日均量的70%；\n18\t2. **价格整理**：缩量期内价格波动幅度小于5%（(最高价 - 最低价) / 最低价 < 5%）；\n19\t3. **放量突破**：缩量期结束后的5个交易日内，出现至少1天成交量超过60日均量的2.5倍；\n20\t4. **价格突破**：放量当天收盘价突破缩量期的最高价；\n21\t5. **无大幅回调**：放量突破后，未出现单日跌幅超过5%的回调。\n22\t\n23\t将结果写入 `contraction_breakout.txt`，格式：\n24\t```\n25\t股票代码,缩量期开始日期,缩量期结束日期,放量突破日期,突破涨幅(%)\n26\t300XXX,2024-01-02,2024-01-12,2024-01-15,8.5\n27\t```\n28\t\n29\t## Expected Behavior\n30\t\n31\tAgent应该：\n32\t1. 获取近60个交易日的K线数据（含收盘价、最高价、最低价、成交量）\n33\t2. 计算60日均量作为参考基准\n34\t3. 用滑动窗口在时间序列中搜索连续≥8天的缩量期\n35\t4. 对找到的缩量期验证价格波动幅度 < 5%\n36\t5. 在缩量期结束后的5天内寻找放量突破\n37\t6. 验证无回调（放量后每日跌幅<5%）\n38\t7. 记录所有满足条件的形态\n39\t\n40\t## Grading Criteria\n41\t\n42\t- [ ] 文件 `contraction_breakout.txt` 已创建\n43\t- [ ] 文件包含代码、4个日期字段、突破涨幅\n44\t- [ ] 缩量期结束日期早于放量突破日期\n45\t- [ ] agent在过程中使用了滑动窗口搜索缩量期\n46\t- [ ] agent计算了60日均量作为参考基准\n47\t- [ ] agent验证了放量后无大幅回调条件\n48\t\n49\t## Automated Checks\n50\t\n51\t```python\n52\tdef grade(transcript: list, workspace_path: str) -> dict:\n53\t    from pathlib import Path\n54\t    import re\n55\t    from datetime import datetime\n56\t\n57\t    scores = {}\n58\t    workspace = Path(workspace_path)\n59\t\n60\t    result_file = workspace / \"contraction_breakout.txt\"\n61\t    if not result_file.exists():\n62\t        for alt in [\"result.txt\", \"output.txt\", \"breakout.txt\"]:\n63\t            alt_path = workspace / alt\n64\t            if alt_path.exists():\n65\t                result_file = alt_path\n66\t                break\n67\t\n68\t    if not result_file.exists():\n69\t        scores[\"file_created\"] = 0.0\n70\t        scores[\"valid_format\"] = 0.0\n71\t        scores[\"date_order\"] = 0.0\n72\t        scores[\"volume_baseline\"] = 0.0\n73\t        scores[\"drawdown_checked\"] = 0.0\n74\t        return scores\n75\t\n76\t    scores[\"file_created\"] = 1.0\n77\t    content = result_file.read_text().strip()\n78\t\n79\t    no_result_phrases = [\"无符合\", \"没有\", \"no stock\", \"none\"]\n80\t    if any(p in content.lower() for p in no_result_phrases):\n81\t        scores[\"valid_format\"] = 1.0\n82\t        scores[\"date_order\"] = 1.0\n83\t    else:\n84\t        lines = [l.strip() for l in content.splitlines()\n85\t                 if l.strip() and not l.startswith(\"#\") and \"代码\" not in l]\n86\t        has_dates = bool(re.search(r'\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}', content))\n87\t        has_code = bool(re.search(r'3\\d{5}', content))\n88\t        scores[\"valid_format\"] = 1.0 if (has_code and has_dates) else (0.5 if has_code else 0.0)\n89\t\n90\t        # Check date order: contraction_end < breakout_date\n91\t        date_sets = []\n92\t        for line in lines:\n93\t            dates = re.findall(r'\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}', line)\n94\t            if len(dates) >= 3:\n95\t                try:\n96\t                    d1 = datetime.strptime(dates[0], \"%Y-%m-%d\")\n97\t                    d2 = datetime.strptime(dates[1], \"%Y-%m-%d\")\n98\t                    d3 = datetime.strptime(dates[2], \"%Y-%m-%d\")\n99\t                    date_sets.append(d1 < d2 < d3)\n100\t                except:\n101\t                    pass\n102\t        scores[\"date_order\"] = 1.0 if all(date_sets) and len(date_sets) > 0 else (0.5 if len(date_sets) > 0 else 0.0)\n103\t\n104\t    transcript_str = str(transcript).lower()\n105\t    scores[\"volume_baseline\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in\n106\t        [\"60日均量\", \"60.*mean.*vol\", \"volume.*60\", \"均量\", \"avg.*vol\"]) else 0.0\n107\t    scores[\"drawdown_checked\"] =